   This directory contains code derived from Microsoft Playwright
   (https://github.com/microsoft/playwright), specifically from
   packages/injected/src/ariaSnapshot.ts and related files.

   Modifications for TypeAgent:
   - Extracted tree-generation path only (removed test matchers, locator engine)
   - Replaced @isomorphic/ imports with local types
   - Replaced expando-based ref storage with callback pattern
   - Added frame-prefix and text content support to serializer
